<table>
  <thead><tr><th>State</th><th>Behavior</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>controls</code> (present)</td><td>Browser renders native play, pause, seek, volume, and fullscreen UI</td></tr>
    <tr><td>(absent)</td><td>No visible controls. Media can only be controlled via JavaScript or autoplay.</td></tr>
